title: Malaysia's Anwar visits Indonesia in his first overseas trip since jail release
text:
Malaysia's Anwar visits Indonesia in his first overseas trip since jail release 7:38pm IST - 01:24
The poltician paid a visit to the former President of Indonesia after being granted full pardon and freed from jail. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
